{"tid":1430051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：支持年輕人繼續尋夢、追夢、築夢和圓夢","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:57:13.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a62ffd9a390ee43f4ac9b7f157a3c33b86c7a3d2","tid":1430051,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190807_20190807-121514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190807_20190807-121514.jpg&h=be0f868d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥早上出席一個國慶展覽開幕禮，致辭時表示，香港近月出現非常不穩定的情況，特區政府一定會與大家一同沉著應對，恢復社會秩序，維護法治，珍惜香港，珍惜一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n她說，面對持續的暴力違法活動，香港社會正需要強大的正能量，她懇請大家堅決捍衞香港法治，支持社會早日回復平靜，讓特區政府可以集中精力發展經濟，改善民生。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，一國兩制是國家堅守的政策，在一國兩制的獨特優勢下，香港受惠於國家高速發展帶來的種種機遇，特區政府會積極融入國家發展大局、參與「一帶一路」及粵港澳大灣區建設，支持年輕人繼續尋夢、追夢、築夢和圓夢，會繼續為年輕人提供更多就業創業機會。<br />\n<br />\n出席開幕禮的包括中聯辦副主任楊健、外交部駐港副特派員宋如安及駐港部隊副政治委員陳亞丁。"},{"pid":"6ffce78b1ba0dc38182cfb41738f828956f8bb5e","tid":1430051,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1150190&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1150190%26csid%3D261_341&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=7625e771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1150190&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"9d50c55bde6f4fe6ec4b7104f725c35a658840f9","tid":1430051,"uid":260035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3776226657fb660bdf5f9d59703dc9a366bb890a","tid":1430051,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:49:18.000Z","msg